title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2016
summary: The Number of Total United States States vehicles to the entering begins at a prominent high level , followed by a dramatical drop to reach the lowest point in April , which reduces to a fifth of the beginning point .
Then the Number remains stable with a slight increase to December .
gold: This graph depicts the total number of United States vehicles entering in Canada during 2016 . The lowest number of vehicles is observed in January , at approximately 640000 . During the following months numbers of entering vehicles steadily increase until reaching the maximum number the year 2016 in July with approximately 1250000 .
